headline: Is Adobe Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Despite Adobe's weak performance relative to the broader Nasdaq Composite over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Adobe Looks Cheap Ahead of Earnings - Short Put Yields are Juicy!
summary: Adobe releases its earnings on Sept. 11, and ADBE stock is down too much. With its strong free cash flow and FCF margins, ADBE stock could be worth 36% more at $485. Short-put yields are very high for less than 1 month.
